<item>
            <title>[LU-1519] discretionary access control overrides should be explicit</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1519</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some ioctls enable overrides of discretionary access controls.  Enabling this behavior should require an explicit action/configuration by the administrator.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
